cument.@Example{The application of the section command}For example the command sequence@Verbatim         @Section{The Author's View}@End-Verbatim would produce the headline of a section with the title '1.1. The Author's View', assumingthat it is the document's first section.@End-Example For this command there is a @Application-Link{ "template" | "GoMan:section-command" } available. @Subsubsection{Subsection}@Label{"Subsection"}@Index{Command Subsection}For this command there is a @Application-Link{ "template" | "GoMan:subsection-command" } available. @Subsubsection{Subsubsection}@Label{"Subsubsection"}@Index{Command Subsubsection}For this command there is a @Application-Link{ "template" | "GoMan:subsubsection-command" } available.@Subsubsection{Figure}@Label{"Figure"}@Index{Command Figure}For this command there is a @Application-Link{ "template" | "GoMan:figure-command" } available. @Subsubsection{Example}@Label{"Example"}@Index{Command Example}For this command there is a @Application-Link{ "template" | "GoMan:example-command" } available.  @Subsubsection{Index}@Label{"Index"}@Index{Command Index}For this command there is a @Application-Link{ "template" | "GoMan:index-command" } available.  @Subsubsection{Label}@Label{"Label"}@Index{Command Label} For this command there is a @Application-Link{ "template" | "GoMan:label-command" } available. @Subsubsection{Link}@Label{"Link"}@Index{Command Link} For this command there is a @Application-Link{ "template" | "GoMan:link-command" } available. @Subsubsection{Document-Link}@Label{"Document-Link"}@Index{Command Document-Link}For this command there is a @Application-Link{ "template" | "GoMan:document-link-command" } available.  @Subsubsection{Application-Link}@Label{"Application-Link"}@Index{Command Application-Link}For this command there is a @Application-Link{ "template" | "GoMan:application-link-command" } available.  @Subsubsection{Item}@Label{